女士 对不起
I'm sorry, Madam.

94
00:05:22,273 --> 00:05:24,272
只有员工才有资格调整展示的衣服
Only members of staff are allowed to adjust the displays.

95
00:05:24,273 --> 00:05:27,273
是不是有什么需要我帮忙的...?
But if there's anything I can help you with...?

