I do not love Clara!

131
00:07:29,273 --> 00:07:33,272
德妮丝 你自己也说了 我们必须小心行事
Denise, you said so yourself, we must tread carefully.

132
00:07:33,273 --> 00:07:36,272
我们所有的努力都是要赢回天堂百货
All of our efforts must go to winning back The Paradise.

133
00:07:36,273 --> 00:07:40,272
如果奥德丽小姐没有离开
If Miss Audrey had not left, if...

134
