848
00:49:21,273 --> 00:49:22,272
当然可以
Yes, of course.

849
00:49:22,273 --> 00:49:24,273
芙罗拉 想去看看后台吗?
Flora, would you like to see backstage?

850
00:49:44,273 --> 00:49:47,272
真是貌美如花余音绕梁啊!
You look beautiful and you sound lovely!

851
00:49:47,273 --> 00:49:49,272
山姆 准备好了吗?
Sam, you ready?

852
00:49:49,273 --> 00:49:53,272
他快好了! 加油山姆 最后的冲刺了
He's nearly there! Come on, Sam, just one last squeeze.

853
00:49:53,273 --> 00:49:55,273
穿进去啦!
I'm in!

854
00:50:00,273 --> 00:50:02,273
最好别他娘的是我想的那样
That better bloody not be what I think it is.

855
00:50:25,273 --> 00:50:28,272
你不觉得模仿你也算一种奉承么?
Don't you know that imitation is a form of flattery?

856
00:50:28,273 --> 00:50:31,272
欢迎来此盛会 女士们先生们 哇噢!
Welcome, ladies and gentlemen. Ooh!

857
00:50:31,273 --> 00:50:33,272
你好啊 帅哥!
Hello, handsome!

858
00:50:33,273 --> 00:50:36,272
现在 女士们先生们 都准备好了吗?
Now, ladies and gentlemen, are we ready for the show?

859
00:50:36,273 --> 00:50:37,272
好了!
Yes!

860
00:50:37,273 --> 00:50:40,272
再问一遍 都准备好了吗?
I said, are we ready for the show?

861
00:50:40,273 --> 00:50:41,272
准备好了!
Yes!

862
00:50:41,273 --> 00:50:44,272
下面有请...
Then I give you...

863
00:50:44,273 --> 00:50:47,273
奇迹大师 亚瑟!
The Amazing Arthur!

864
00:50:54,273 --> 00:50:56,273
威斯顿先生 不介意的话借用下你的帽子
Mr Weston, your hat, if you wouldn't mind.

865
00:50:57,273 --> 00:50:59,273
给
There you go.

866
00:51:08,273 --> 00:51:10,273
大力士 沃尔多!
The Mighty Waldo!

867
00:51:29,273 --> 00:51:30,272
# 有天清晨 #
Early one morning

868
00:51:30,273 --> 00:51:33,272
# 朝阳初升 #
Just as the sun was rising,

869
00:51:33,273 --> 00:51:34,316
# 我听闻 
I heard 

870
00:51:34,317 --> 00:51:37,272
年轻女孩在山谷中扬起的美妙歌声 #
a young maid singing in the valley below

871
00:51:37,273 --> 00:51:40,272
# 噢 别欺骗我 #
Oh, don't deceive me

872
00:51:40,273 --> 00:51:43,272
# 噢 别离开我 #
Oh, never leave me

873
00:51:43,273 --> 00:51:48,273
# 你如何忍心欺侮这可怜的少女至深 #
How could you use a poor maiden so? 

874
00:52:17,273 --> 00:52:19,273
真不错 乔纳斯先生
That's good, Mr Jonas.

875
00:52:35,273 --> 00:52:37,273
太精彩了
Bravo.

876
00:52:51,273 --> 00:52:53,272
注意了 女士们先生们
Now, ladies and gentleman.

877
00:52:53,273 --> 00:52:57,939
请静待我们的最终场 
Please pray silence for our final act, 

878
00:52:57,940 --> 00:53:00,273
压轴戏来了
and the highlight of our show.

879
00:53:01,273 --> 00:53:06,273
小神童 芙罗拉・威斯顿小姐!
The Infant Prodigy - Miss Flora Weston!

880
00:53:13,273 --> 00:53:15,272
她要表演什么?
What is she about?

881
00:53:15,273 --> 00:53:17,272
大伙们 只能问十个问题
Ladies and gentlemen, ten questions only.

882
00:53:17,273 --> 00:53:19,272
我们没有多少时间了
We only have time for ten questions

883
00:53:19,273 --> 00:53:21,272
所以第一个 谁先来个热场的
so that will come on a first come, first served basis.

884
00:53:21,273 --> 00:53:22,272
谁呢...
So...

885
00:53:22,273 --> 00:53:23,272
就你了
Yes?

886
00:53:23,273 --> 00:53:27,272
请问 秘鲁的首都是?
I would like to know, what is the capital of Peru?

887
00:53:27,273 --> 00:53:28,273
利马
Lima.

888
00:53:35,273 --> 00:53:38,272
我想问问小神童
I would like to ask the Infant Prodigy,

889
00:53:38,273 --> 00:53:40,272
"雨伞"用法语怎么说?
how do you say "umbrella" in French?

890
00:53:40,273 --> 00:53:42,273
Parapluie
Parapluie.

891
00:53:47,273 --> 00:53:50,272
你能说出一种化学元素吗?
Can you name me one chemical element?

892
00:53:50,273 --> 00:53:51,273
铜
Copper.

893
00:53:56,273 --> 00:53:59,272
北美最大的河流是?
What is the largest river in North America?

894
00:53:59,273 --> 00:54:00,273
密西西比河
The Mississippi River.

895
00:54:02,273 --> 00:54:04,272
你能拼出chrysanthemum(菊花)么?
Can you spell the word chrysanthemum?

896
00:54:04,273 --> 00:54:09,273
C-H-R-Y-S-A-N-T-H-E-M-U-M
C-H-R-Y-S-A-N-T-H-E-M-U-M.

897
00:54:11,273 --> 00:54:13,273
苏格兰的首府是?
Can you tell me the capital of Scotland?

898
00:54:15,273 --> 00:54:16,273
爱丁堡
Edinburgh.

899
00:54:22,273 --> 00:54:24,273
稍等一下
Excuse me?

900
00:54:30,273 --> 00:54:33,273
我想问小神童一个问题
I should like to ask the Infant Prodigy a question.

901
00:54:34,273 --> 00:54:37,272
克里斯多夫・哥伦布
In what year did Christopher 

902
00:54:37,273 --> 00:54:40,272
哪年发现新大陆的?
Columbus discover America?

903
00:54:40,273 --> 00:54:41,273
1492年
1492.

904
00:54:49,273 --> 00:54:51,273
她是你的荣耀
She is a credit to you.

905
00:54:59,273 --> 00:55:02,273
做得好 芙罗拉小姐 来这边坐
Well done, Miss Flora, go and sit down.

906
00:55:06,273 --> 00:55:08,272
感谢你们的到场 女士们先生们
Thank you all for coming, ladies and gentlemen.

907
00:55:08,273 --> 00:55:13,273
今晚要特别感谢两个人 威斯顿先生
Now we have two people to thank for this evening. Mr Weston.

908
00:55:20,273 --> 00:55:23,273
以及女装部的德妮丝・洛维特
And Denise Lovett of Ladieswear!

909
00:55:39,273 --> 00:55:42,272
接手吧 那职位归你了
Have it. Have the job.

910
00:55:42,273 --> 00:55:45,273
但我得提醒你 你会失去你男人
But I'll tell you something - you'll lose the man.

911
00:55:53,273 --> 00:55:58,273
德妮丝 你惊艳了我们所有人
Denise. You have dazzled us all.

912
00:55:59,273 --> 00:56:01,273
我只想惊艳到你
I only wanted to dazzle you.

913
00:56:02,273 --> 00:56:05,273
我不能忍受我们分开了 我受不了
I can't bear it when we're apart. I can't bear it.

914
00:56:13,273 --> 00:56:14,273
去吧 大家都等着你呢
Go. Your public awaits.

915
00:56:29,273 --> 00:56:33,272
莫里 我想女装部的新主管可以定下了
Moray? I think we've found our new Head Of Ladieswear.

916
00:56:33,273 --> 00:56:35,272
当心了 莫里
Only be careful, Moray.

917
00:56:35,273 --> 00:56:37,273
光彩夺目的德妮丝可能会掩盖住你的光芒
Denise shines so bright she may yet outshine you.

918
00:56:40,273 --> 00:56:44,273
我觉得或许你都达不到她今天的成就
I don't think even you could have achieved what she did today.

919
00:57:01,273 --> 00:57:02,272
我是女装部主管
I am Head of Ladieswear.

920
00:57:02,273 --> 00:57:03,272
你得尽快进入角色
You need to step into the role now.

921
00:57:03,273 --> 00:57:05,272
这意味着你做的决定可能不招人喜爱
That means making decisions that others won't like.

922
00:57:05,273 --> 00:57:07,272
苏西 照顾一下小姑娘
Susy, please attend to the young lady.

923
00:57:07,273 --> 00:57:11,272
这些就交给你了 现在我要和莫里去喝杯咖啡
I will leave it with you while I have a coffee with Moray.

924
00:57:11,273 --> 00:57:14,272
你算什么 你就是一个被宠坏了的娇娇女!
You're just a spoiled little nothing, that's what you are!

925
00:57:14,273 --> 00:57:15,272
你个熊孩子!
You are a child!

926
00:57:15,273 --> 00:57:17,272
苏西 到餐厅去
Susy, go down to the Refectory right now.

927
00:57:17,273 --> 00:57:18,272
我要找妈妈
I want Mama.

928
00:57:18,273 --> 00:57:21,272
你要为我孩子蒙受的耻辱主持公道
It was you who presided over this humiliation of my child.

929
00:57:21,273 --> 00:57:23,272
你怎么处置那女孩?
What do you propose to do about this girl?

930
00:57:23,273 --> 00:57:26,272
你自己想要这个职位 这不是过家家
You wanted this position. It is not all tea parties.

931
00:57:26,273 --> 00:57:29,273
你得收拾东西...走人
You must collect your belongings... and go.

